Hi David,

I have been running the T in the fuel line for a good many years now and 
have not had any issues with it. I have also used a T in a bench-test 
rig I built in winter 2007 and it worked fine as well. I would 
definitely choose a T over a tank swap if I was doing another.

Happy Trails,

